25:23.609 --> 25:27.395
♪ I THINK BACK TO WHEN I WAS YOUNGER

25:28.439 --> 25:32.661
♪ SHE GIVES ME HOPE
AND SAYS MAKE THE MOST OF TIME ♪

25:32.792 --> 25:37.579
♪ THE DAYS DON'T GET ANY LONGER

25:37.710 --> 25:41.322
♪ THAT'S WHAT IT MEANS TO BELIEVE

