32:43.178 --> 32:46.877
OKAY.
YOU'RE DOING GOOD HERE.

32:47.008 --> 32:48.531
NICE AND WARM.

32:50.185 --> 32:51.012
WE'RE DOING GOOD.

32:52.013 --> 32:53.319
