32:54.537 --> 32:55.974
WE'RE DOING REAL GOOD.

32:57.584 --> 32:58.977
DOING REAL GOOD.

33:57.078 --> 33:59.994
HOT ROCKS! HOT ROCKS!

34:00.125 --> 34:02.475
GET YOUR HOT ROCKS HERE.

34:02.605 --> 34:04.607
I GOT SOME HOT ROCKS HERE.

34:06.870 --> 34:08.829
OKAY, OKAY.

34:08.958 --> 34:11.571
ONE, TWO.

34:15.748 --> 34:18.621
-LOOK, OVER ON THE BEACH.
THERE'S SMOKE.

34:23.626 --> 34:26.455
-IT'S THEM!
IT'S GOTTA BE THEM.

34:31.373 --> 34:34.376
-THESE WILL KEEP YOU NICE
AND WARM. NICE--

34:35.159 --> 34:37.639
-[HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING]

34:37.771 --> 34:40.382
-I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

34:57.530 --> 35:00.446
HEY! HEY!

35:17.071 --> 35:19.943
OUR FLIGHT IS BOARDING.

35:21.031 --> 35:23.208
COME ON. ALL RIGHT.

35:26.863 --> 35:28.169
[GRUNTS]

35:41.530 --> 35:42.444
YEAH.

35:43.402 --> 35:44.664
WE'RE GOING HOME.

35:46.361 --> 35:47.667
WE'RE GOING HOME.

36:30.710 --> 36:32.146
-HI.
-HEY.

36:34.801 --> 36:35.671
HOW YOU DOING?

36:36.542 --> 36:37.760
-OKAY.

36:37.891 --> 36:39.632
-DOC SAYS YOU'RE DOING
ALL RIGHT.

36:40.198 --> 36:42.330
-AW, WHAT DOES HE KNOW?

36:46.726 --> 36:48.815
WHEN I FIRST WOKE UP,
I THOUGHT IT WAS A DREAM.

36:50.469 --> 36:52.906
THEN I REMEMBERED YOU HOLDING ME
BY THE FIRE,

36:53.472 --> 36:56.649
KEEPING ME AWAKE,
KEEPING ME ALIVE.

37:00.566 --> 37:02.655
-IT WAS TOUCH-AND-GO THERE
FOR A WHILE.

37:03.569 --> 37:05.527
-THE FIRST THING I'M GONNA
DO WHEN I GET OUT OF HERE

37:05.658 --> 37:07.921
IS RECOMMEND YOU
FOR A MEDAL OF VALOR.

37:09.357 --> 37:11.054
-NO ONE WOULD BELIEVE THE STORY.

37:11.185 --> 37:14.406
-I DON'T CARE.
I'M WRITING IT ALL DOWN.

37:15.276 --> 37:17.147
IF NOTHING ELSE,
I'LL SELL IT TO A MAGAZINE.

37:17.887 --> 37:20.977
-WE COULD CALL IT
"VACATION FROM HELL."

37:24.372 --> 37:27.332
-YOU'LL HAVE TO HELP ME
WITH THE BLANK SPOTS.

37:28.550 --> 37:30.857
I WAS DELIRIOUS HALF THE TIME.

37:31.510 --> 37:33.947
-YEAH, I KNOW.

37:34.077 --> 37:36.645
THERE WAS A COUPLE OF MOMENTS
I WAS PRETTY DELIRIOUS MYSELF.

37:40.780 --> 37:42.216
-THERE'S ONE THING
I DO REMEMBER.

37:43.217 --> 37:44.087
-WHAT?

37:46.176 --> 37:47.526
-I NEVER SAID "THANK YOU."

37:52.748 --> 37:53.575
THANK YOU, MITCH.

38:14.901 --> 38:17.425
-YOU REALLY THINK WE COULD SELL
THE STORY TO A MAGAZINE?

38:17.556 --> 38:23.213
-OH, MITCH, STOP. OW!
DOCTOR, HELP ME FROM THIS GUY.

38:24.563 --> 38:26.608
OW. STOP.

38:32.962 --> 38:34.007
-MATTHEW:
CJ.

38:38.185 --> 38:39.621
WHY ARE YOU AVOIDING ME?

38:39.752 --> 38:42.624
-I'M NOT AVOIDING YOU.
-YES, YOU ARE.

38:43.582 --> 38:45.018
IT'S THE LOAN, ISN'T IT?

38:45.845 --> 38:47.934
YOU FEEL UNCOMFORTABLE
BECAUSE YOU OWE ME MONEY.

38:48.674 --> 38:52.330
LOOK, CJ, I DON'T WANT THIS
TO PUT A STRAIN ON
OUR RELATIONSHIP.

38:52.460 --> 38:54.636
YOU CAN PAY ME BACK
WHENEVER YOU WANT.

38:54.767 --> 38:56.508
JUST DON'T SKIP TOWN, OKAY?

38:58.771 --> 39:00.555
-THAT'S VERY SWEET OF YOU,
MATTHEW.

39:05.908 --> 39:09.782
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT? I THINK
I'M GONNA SETTLE UP RIGHT NOW.

39:10.652 --> 39:12.262
-WHERE DID YOU GET
ALL THAT CASH?

39:13.568 --> 39:15.222
-I FOUND THE CHIP THAT
THE PIT BOSS GAVE ME.

39:15.353 --> 39:17.659
I WENT BACK INTO THE CASINO
AND I WON IT ALL BACK.

39:18.965 --> 39:20.096
-YOU'RE UNREAL.

39:20.793 --> 39:22.447
-$5,000, PAYMENT IN FULL.

39:24.666 --> 39:26.973
-AND WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO
WITH THE REST OF THAT?

39:27.887 --> 39:29.628
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA GO ON,
A SHOPPING SPREE?

39:30.280 --> 39:32.413
-WELL, I THINK THAT'S WHAT
I WOULD HAVE DONE BEFORE,

39:33.849 --> 39:36.939
BUT I THINK THAT THE ONLY WAY
I'M GONNA GET RID OF THIS
GAMBLING PROBLEM IS

39:37.070 --> 39:41.379
TO GIVE THE MONEY AWAY.
-GIVE THE MONEY AWAY? TO WHO?

39:43.990 --> 39:46.862
-HEAL THE BAY.
-HEAL THE BAY?

39:47.689 --> 39:51.040
-YEAH. YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT OF
WHAT WAS MOST IMPORTANT TO ME,

39:52.172 --> 39:53.391
AND WHAT I WANTED,

39:54.217 --> 39:55.436
AND THIS IS IT.

39:56.916 --> 40:00.920
THE WATER, THE BEACH,
MY FRIENDS.

40:01.529 --> 40:03.270
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
THEY'RE ALWAYS GONNA BE THERE.

40:05.533 --> 40:06.665
YOU THINK I'M DOING
THE RIGHT THING?

40:07.883 --> 40:09.319
-YEAH, I DO.

40:09.450 --> 40:10.495
I THINK YOU'RE DOING
THE RIGHT THING.

40:14.542 --> 40:17.240
-SO, OLD GREAT GIGOLO, HOW MUCH
DID YOU GET MRS. KENILWORTH

40:17.371 --> 40:19.417
TO INVEST IN WINDOWS BY GUIDO?

40:19.547 --> 40:22.289
-PLEASE, CAN WE TALK ABOUT
SOMETHING ELSE?
-OH, WHAT HAPPENED?

40:22.420 --> 40:25.248
THINGS DIDN'T WORK OUT?
-WELL, AS IT TURNS OUT,

40:25.379 --> 40:28.730
SHE WASN'T INTERESTED
IN MY BUSINESS. ONLY MY BODY.

40:29.470 --> 40:32.691
-[LAUGHS]
COULDN'T RESIST YOUR CHARMS.

40:32.821 --> 40:36.738
-[BLOWS]
THERE YOU GO.

40:36.869 --> 40:40.133
NO SPECKS, NO STREAKS,
NO SMUDGES.

40:40.263 --> 40:42.396
THE PERFECT WINDOW.

40:44.050 --> 40:45.791
-GUIDO!

40:47.532 --> 40:49.185
-OH, NO!

40:49.838 --> 40:52.188
MITCH, CALL THE POLICE!
MRS. KENILWORTH, GLAD
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

40:52.319 --> 40:54.364
-THERE YOU ARE, YOU LITTLE
DEVIL. COME BACK HERE.

40:54.495 --> 40:57.933
[SHOUTING]

